                        <div id="page-title">
                            2020“古代传说”征文竞赛
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>2020夏季竞赛：“古代传说”征文竞赛！</span></h1>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;">自古以来，中外历史中便不乏神话传说的身影；或口耳相传，或见于典籍，这些被人们代代传承的瑰丽想象在文学中占据了重要的一席之地，也催生了无数的优秀创作。现在，你将执笔，以见证这些奇诡的故事能与基金会世界观碰撞出怎样的火花。</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="background-color: lightyellow; font-size: 150%; border: dashed 3px brown; border-radius: 3px; text-align: center; width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
<p>最终，前三名为以下作品以及其作者！</p>
<p>第一名：<a href="/zuirenyu">曾经存在过的故事（三则）</a>(+79)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flying-jellyfish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1925789); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1925789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599707941" alt="Flying Jellyfish" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1925789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flying-jellyfish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1925789); return false;">Flying Jellyfish</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>第二名：<a href="/scp-cn-1838">SCP-CN-1838</a>(+69)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/day-by-die" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3626255); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3626255&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599707941" alt="day by die" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3626255)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/day-by-die" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3626255); return false;">day by die</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>第三名：<a href="/scp-cn-974">SCP-CN-974</a>(+53)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599707941" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span>与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salty-dragon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5389867); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5389867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599707941" alt="Salty Dragon" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5389867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salty-dragon" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5389867); return false;">Salty Dragon</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>请诸位得奖者与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/holy-darklight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1768886); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1768886&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1599707941" alt="Holy_Darklight" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1768886)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/holy-darklight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1768886); return false;">Holy_Darklight</a></span>联络获取奖品。</p>
</div>
